Package: MetaTX
Type: Package
Title: To sketch a transcriptomic view of RNA-related features
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-01-21
Author: Yue Wang
Maintainer: Yue Wang <15905529958@163.com>
Description: The metaTX package can estimate the distribution of RNA-related genomic features. It incorporates the coordinate inconsistency, width variation and isoform ambiguity into consideration, and its EM algorithm performs empirical correc-tion of biases with current existing methods. 
